cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.LG. 

The paper presents an autonomous unmanned aerial vehicle (UAV) landing system based on visual navigation, which involves the use of computer vision and robotics. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.RO (Robotics), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) as image processing is a key component of the system. The system also involves decision-making and control, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the system's performance is evaluated using experimental results, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning).
